dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.swcomponenttemplate.swcinternalbehavior.dataelements

Interface IDataReceivePoint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable

    public interface IDataReceivePoint
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IDataReceivePoint: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    A DataReceivePoint allows a RunnableEntity to explicitly query for received information, thereby blocking write access to the same information only for a very brief period.
